  <section>
    <title lang='en'>Accessing your reader's account</title>

    <para lang='en'>To access your reader's account, you need to know your reader's card
    n° (the figures printed under your card's barcode) and your password. If
    you haven't changed your password, it is by default identical to your
    reader's card n°.</para>

